data.description: SPACIOUS 4BD 3BA HOME IN NEWPORT SUBDIVISION  This home has it all. Main living area is open and airy. Pass through window in kitchen keeps chef in the action while entertaining. Plenty of cabinet and counter space in this beautifully upgraded kitchen. Family room opens to good size fenced backyard that would be great for kids to play or just to relax and have a BBQ. Plus the back gate opens up to a lagoon. Now let's talk bedrooms. Three bedrooms downstairs including a large primary bedroom with a private bath. Upstairs is another huge bedroom with a private bath which could be a bonus room. We're talking office, den, man cave, she shed, game room, whatever you desire. Large two car garage with work station. Fantastic location near shopping, Gulfstream and airport. 2 miles from I-95 and 4 miles from the Tanger Outlet mall and near all of the restaurants and shops on Pooler Parkway. 20 minutes to Hunter Army Airfield, 6 miles from Savannah International Airport, 8 miles from Gulfstream.
